Let bi be the bandwidth between eNodeB and SMD i, and the bandwidth is allocated to each SMD orthogonally in this system. Thus, there is no interference among the SMDs. The uplink channel gain from SMD i to eNodeB is denoted as hi. The uplink transmission power of SMD i to eNodeB is piu\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
